---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Wholesale — Acme Coffee Roasters">
  <p class="eyebrow">For cafés &amp; restaurants</p>
  <h1>Wholesale</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    We roast for two cafés and four restaurants in Springfield. We have room for
    one or two more. If you run a bar and want a house bean, get in touch.
  </p>

  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <dl class="facts">
    <dt>Minimum</dt><dd>10 lb / week, standing order.</dd>
    <dt>Schedule</dt><dd>Roasted Tuesday, delivered Wednesday morning.</dd>
    <dt>Pricing</dt><dd>$14–$18 / lb depending on the lot. No shipping charges inside Springfield.</dd>
    <dt>Terms</dt><dd>Net-15. Invoiced monthly.</dd>
    <dt>Exclusivity</dt><dd>We don't ask for it. Carry whoever you want.</dd>
  </dl>

  <h2>What we can do for you</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>A standing house bean, rotated seasonally.</li>
    <li>A featured single-origin on a 4–6 week cycle.</li>
    <li>A custom blend matched to your espresso setup — we'll come cup with you.</li>
    <li>Basic brew training for new staff, free for accounts.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Next step</h2>
  <p>
    Email <a href="mailto:wholesale@acmecoffee.example">wholesale@acmecoffee.example</a>
    with what you're pouring now and what you'd want to change. We'll send a
    sample flight within the week.
  </p>
</Base>
